Relocation Laws in Andorra

You may envision yourself living in Andorra and raising your children in as loving an environment as possible. However, it is important to understand how the law views any moves you make relative to an international divorce decree in Andorra.

The tendency would be to follow your children if you could; however, it is imperative that you do not travel or move without first consulting your international divorce attorney in Andorra. Relocation is added cause for concern for local authorities and is thus carried even more heavily against you in the court system in Andorra.

Your international divorce lawyer in Andorra will provide you with professional legal guidance in all areas of your life, not just regarding a foreign court decree or custody issues. When caught unaware by relocation laws, you could find yourself in serious trouble in Andorra.
